{"tid":2265117,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"返工成日擔擔抬抬搞到腰痛","createTime":"2020-10-31T07:32:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-31T21:08:43.000Z","uid":368023,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a27c4b2816e193dd73e0a5cbf4b60775b886e623","tid":2265117,"uid":368023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T07:32:46.000Z","msg":"如題 做嘢成日都要彎腰然後抬啲好重嘅嘢<br />\n不過係我男朋友 唔係我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢份工淨係做咗4個月左右，條腰已經開始痛<br />\n宜家佢淨係keep住用日本啲痠痛貼，話貼完會好啲冇咁痛<br />\n但我覺得長遠落去都唔係辦法，用嗰啲貼只係治標唔治本<br />\n<br />\n我好擔心佢，驚做耐啲條腰就痛一世，但佢好似完全唔care自己條腰咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n上網揾過下，見多數人都係做物理治療/去睇跌打<br />\n但佢唔喺香港，嗰邊好似冇乜跌打師傅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n請問有冇巴絲試過腰痛，介唔介意分享下點醫返好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好驚佢再咁落去會痛到連嘢都扑唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9aaece631bd61d0f2675bbcae9dfe2792bb87eb7","tid":2265117,"uid":11598,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T07:37:42.000Z","msg":"首先 搬嘢抬嘢一定唔可以彎腰搬<br />\n會腰痛即係姿勢錯晒<br />\n一定要用大腿發力<br />\n唔知你男友持續咗幾耐<br />\n長期錯姿勢會搞到關節啲啫喱蝕晒"},{"pid":"d79796921da9fd2da30ebaab3ab12db31eec5e3c","tid":2265117,"uid":140450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T07:44:38.000Z","msg":"其一 唔可以彎腰，因為腰發力唔係用曲既角度而係要保持直立先可以俾其他肌群support <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其二 如果已經開始痛 係發炎已經開始，貼止痛只係短期，長遠都係要多做運動強化核心同背（p.s. 練背最好練埋胸）"},{"pid":"4f51a90e0d772bf9a7e6f83b9cd0f49ca1d8d2bb","tid":2265117,"uid":373567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T16:34:30.000Z","msg":"你男朋友做地盤？"},{"pid":"6352295838e3008d914183c5272ac16ba2aab94b","tid":2265117,"uid":273006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T16:45:25.000Z","msg":"拿拿聲同佢睇物理治療啦<br />\n治療師會教佢正確搬嘢方法<br />\n千其唔好浪費錢去睇鐵打"},{"pid":"022b9f9de9ff6ac2b654b83e0d00b75c300233cc","tid":2265117,"uid":189796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T21:08:43.000Z","msg":"叫你男朋友快d改正，我就係咁無理到，而家椎間盤突出"}]}